sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects usage of a base64 encoded "FromBase64String" cmdlet in a process command line
Detects usage of the "FromBase64String" function in the commandline which is used to decode a base64 encoded string
Detects usage of "Reflection.Assembly" load functions to dynamically load assemblies in memory
Detects the creation of a new office macro files on the systems

threat_severity.level_description: Severity MEDIUM because it was considered trojan.

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp any any -> any $HTTP_PORTS ( msg:"POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt"; flow:to_server,established; http_header; content:"Host:",fast_pattern,nocase; pcre:"/^Host\x3a\s*(?:(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\.){3}(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\s*:?\s*\d*\s*$/ims"; service:http; reference:url,www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec15.html; classtype:policy-violation; sid:50447; rev:1; )

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: (http_inspect) URI has two-byte or three-byte UTF-8 encoding
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert ( gid:119; sid:6; rev:3; msg:"(http_inspect) URI has two-byte or three-byte UTF-8 encoding"; metadata: rule-type preproc; reference:cve,2008-2938; reference:cve,2009-1535; reference:url,www.microsoft.com/technet/security/bulletin/ms09-020.mspx; service:http; classtype:not-suspicious;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: FILE-IDENTIFY Microsoft Windows Visual Basic script file download request
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET $HTTP_PORTS ( msg:"FILE-IDENTIFY Microsoft Windows Visual Basic script file download request"; flow:to_server,established; http_uri; content:".vbs",fast_pattern,nocase; pcre:"/\x2evbs([\?\x5c\x2f]|$)/ims"; metadata:policy max-detect-ips drop; service:http; reference:url,en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vbs; classtype:misc-activity; sid:18758; rev:12; )

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: TGI HUNT b64 exe in HTTP (UTF8)
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert http any any -> any any (msg:"TGI HUNT b64 exe in HTTP (UTF8)"; flow:established; content:"TVqQAAMAAAAEAAAA//8AAL"; fast_pattern; classtype:bad-unknown; sid:2610768; rev:1;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp any any -> any any (msg:"TGI HUNT b64 exe in TCP (UTF8)"; flow:established; content:"TVqQAAMAAAAEAAAA//8AAL"; fast_pattern; classtype:bad-unknown; sid:2610776; rev:1;)
